INSERT INTO `heroes` (`id`, `images`, `names`, `roles`, `specialities`, `lane`, `desc`) VALUES
(1, 'https://gamedaim.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Miya-Mobile-Legends.jpg', 'Miya', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'Miya, a prodigious archer with unparalleled precision, emerged from a humble village, armed with a burning desire to protect her homeland. With swift movements and deadly arrows, she embarked on a journey to vanquish evil. Along the way, she formed alliances with fellow warriors, forging a bond of unity and strength. Through countless battles, she unleashed her divine archery, striking fear into the hearts of her enemies. With unwavering resolve, she confronted a tyrant, engaging in a breathtaking showdown. Ultimately, her arrows found their mark, liberating her land and earning her the title of a legendary hero, forever etching her name in the annals of Mobile Legends.'),
(2, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/04/26/152794841.jpg', 'Balmond', 'Fighter', 'Damage & Regen', 'Exp', 'Balmond, the indomitable barbarian, hailed from a distant realm, where strength and valor were revered above all else. With his massive axe and insatiable thirst for battle, he embarked on a relentless quest to prove his might. Through countless clashes, Balmond\'s raw power and unwavering ferocity became legendary, striking fear into the hearts of his foes. However, deep within his untamed heart, a glimmer of compassion flickered, urging him to seek redemption for his past transgressions. With newfound purpose, Balmond joined forces with fellow heroes, channeling his brute strength towards the greater good. Together, they battled against darkness, restoring hope and justice to the realm of Mobile Legends, forever solidifying Balmond\'s legacy as a fearsome warrior with a heart that burned brighter than his raging flames.'),
(3, 'https://media.suara.com/pictures/970x544/2022/09/23/69424-hero-saber-mobile-legends.jpg', 'Saber', 'Assassin', 'Charge & Reap', 'Jungler', 'Saber, the swift and deadly assassin, emerged from the shadows, driven by an insatiable thirst for vengeance. Once a noble knight betrayed by his comrades, Saber embraced the path of darkness to seek retribution. With his twin blades slicing through the air, he became a relentless force, hunting down those who wronged him. His lightning-fast strikes and cunning maneuvers struck fear into the hearts of his enemies, leaving no room for escape. As Saber\'s journey unfolded, he discovered that revenge alone could not heal his wounded soul. Guided by newfound allies, he embraced redemption, turning his lethal skills towards protecting the innocent and upholding justice. Through his transformation, Saber transcended his tragic past, becoming a beacon of hope and redemption in the realm of Mobile Legends, forever remembered as a formidable assassin with a noble purpose.'),
(4, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/alice-gridgamesid-scaled.jpeg', 'Alice', 'Mage & Tank', 'Charge & Regen', 'Mid', 'Alice, the enigmatic vampire queen, emerged from the shadows of the night, captivating all who encountered her with her ethereal beauty and mystical powers. Haunted by a tragic past, she sought solace in the depths of darkness, where she honed her mastery over the arcane arts. With her mesmerizing abilities to drain life force and command shadows, Alice became an embodiment of both beauty and terror. Yet, deep within her immortal heart, a longing for connection and understanding burned, driving her to venture beyond her solitary existence. As fate would have it, Alice crossed paths with a band of valiant heroes, who saw the flicker of humanity within her. Together, they faced formidable foes, unraveling ancient mysteries and forging unbreakable bonds. Through their shared battles, Alice discovered her true purpose ? to protect the innocent and embrace her dual nature as both a creature of darkness and a source of light. With her newfound allies, she embarked on a journey to bring balance to the world of Mobil'),
(5, 'https://www.ligagame.tv/images/Nana-Hero-Mobile-Legends_4f22c.jpg', 'Nana', 'Mage & Support', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Nana, the mischievous yet kind-hearted mage, possessed a unique gift for wielding magical spells. Hailing from a mystical forest, she was entrusted with the protection of ancient secrets. With her adorable companion, NeNe, by her side, Nana embarked on a whimsical adventure. Through her enchanting abilities and playful nature, she brought laughter and wonder to all who crossed her path. Yet, when darkness threatened to engulf the land, Nana\'s true strength shone through. With a flick of her wand, she unleashed potent spells, transforming her enemies into helpless creatures. Guided by her compassion, Nana used her magic to heal and support her allies, becoming an irreplaceable asset in battles. Her presence illuminated the battlefield, turning the tides in favor of justice and harmony. As a beloved guardian of the forest, Nana\'s legacy in the realm of Mobile Legends would forever be remembered for her enchanting spirit and unwavering dedication to protecting those she held dear.'),
(6, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/tigreal-mobile-legend-ksatria-cahaya-yang-tak-terkalahkan-scaled-1.jpg', 'Tigreal', 'Tank & Support', 'Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Tigreal, the noble warrior of justice, hailed from a kingdom where honor and righteousness reigned supreme. Clad in his magnificent armor and wielding his mighty lance, he devoted his life to protecting the weak and upholding the principles of chivalry. With unwavering determination, Tigreal embarked on a perilous journey, confronting the forces of darkness that threatened to plunge the land into chaos. His unyielding courage and unwavering loyalty inspired his comrades, rallying them to join his cause. Through countless battles, Tigreal\'s indomitable spirit and impeccable leadership guided his allies to victory. Even in the face of adversity, he remained resolute, shielding his companions from harm and striking down his foes with righteous fury. With each triumph, Tigreal\'s legend grew, becoming a symbol of hope and a beacon of justice in the realm of Mobile Legends, forever etching his name in the annals of heroism.'),
(7, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/alucard-mobile-legends.jpg', 'Alucard', 'Fighter & Assassin', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Alucard, the brooding vampire hunter, was haunted by a tragic past that shaped his unwavering resolve to eradicate the forces of evil. Armed with his cursed sword, Alucard embarked on a relentless crusade to vanquish the creatures of the night that threatened the realm of Mobile Legends. With unparalleled skill and agility, he danced through the battlefield, unleashing swift and devastating strikes upon his enemies. However, beneath his stoic exterior, a glimmer of humanity still flickered within him, a reminder of the love he once knew. As he fought alongside his allies, Alucard\'s redemption grew closer with each fallen foe. With each victory, he found solace and a renewed purpose, vowing to protect the innocent and ensure that darkness would never prevail. In the end, Alucard\'s name became synonymous with both fear and hope, forever etching his legacy as a legendary hero in the annals of Mobile Legends.'),
(8, 'https://cms.hybrid.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/c7b32bfcf8b8024ca629cd790d411c94_karinaspiderlily-scaled.jpg', 'Karina', 'Assassin', 'Reap & Magic Damage', 'Jungler', 'Karina, the enigmatic Shadow Blade, emerged from the shadows with a single-minded mission?to exact vengeance upon those who had wronged her family. With her deadly dual daggers and unparalleled agility, she became a formidable assassin in the realm of Mobile Legends. Driven by her tragic past, Karina cloaked herself in darkness, embracing her role as an agent of retribution. Her swift strikes were swift and precise, leaving her enemies in a state of terror and confusion. But beneath her cold exterior, Karina harbored a conflicted soul, torn between her thirst for revenge and the flickering light of compassion within her heart. As she ventured further into the realm, Karina encountered heroes who saw past her darkness, offering her a chance at redemption. Through their unwavering support, she began to question her path, finding a glimmer of hope amidst the shadows. Determined to protect the innocent and restore balance, Karina wielded her lethal blades not just for vengeance, but for justice. Her journey would'),
(9, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/2022/04/MLBB_Akai_revamp.jpg', 'Akai', 'Tank & Support', 'Guard & Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Akai, the playful panda warrior, was a beloved figure in the realm of Mobile Legends. Endowed with incredible strength and a mischievous spirit, he enchanted both allies and foes alike. Akai\'s journey began in the distant bamboo forests, where he trained tirelessly to master the art of combat. With his mighty fists and agile movements, he swiftly rose to become a formidable force on the battlefield. But it was his unwavering loyalty and infectious charm that truly set him apart. Akai\'s jovial nature brought smiles to the faces of his companions, fostering a sense of unity and camaraderie. Despite his playful demeanor, Akai possessed a deep sense of justice and would fiercely defend the weak and innocent. Throughout his adventures, he encountered challenges that tested his resolve, but he faced them head-on with unyielding determination. Akai\'s legacy as a protector and a source of laughter echoed throughout the land, leaving a lasting impression on all who crossed his path. He taught us that strength and joy '),
(10, 'https://img.esportsku.com/wp-content/uploads//2019/08/9f58b696a1b96eae64dda078375581ea_Mobile-Legends-Franco.jpg', 'Franco', 'Tank & Support', 'Initiator & Control', 'Roamer', 'Franco, the imposing Iron Hook, was a fearsome figure on the battlefield of Mobile Legends. Towering over his enemies, he brandished his massive anchor with ruthless determination. Franco\'s origins were shrouded in mystery, but his reputation as a relentless pursuer of justice was unmatched. With his mighty hook and a devastating power, he relentlessly sought out those who threatened the innocent. His precise aim and unyielding grip made him a nightmare for his adversaries, as they could never escape his grasp. However, beneath his stoic exterior, Franco carried a heavy burden, haunted by the memories of past battles. Despite his rugged appearance, he possessed a compassionate heart, always striving to protect the weak and downtrodden. With every swing of his anchor, he fought for a brighter future, embodying the unwavering spirit of a true hero. Franco\'s legend grew as tales of his unwavering resolve and unbreakable will spread throughout the realm, forever cementing his place as a guardian of justice in the'),
(11, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRNPTGSmgBHqIL8iILxYf9pwi5vesODvWk7pgqsLLw3&s', 'Bane', 'Fighter & Mage', 'Push & Burst', 'Exp', 'Bane, the dreaded Lord of the Seven Seas, ruled the waters of the Mobile Legends realm with an iron fist. Born from the depths of the ocean, he commanded a mighty fleet and instilled fear into the hearts of sailors and warriors alike. Bane\'s colossal presence was matched only by the power of his enchanted cannon, which unleashed devastating salvos upon his enemies. With each blast, his foes trembled and quaked. Bane\'s thirst for conquest knew no bounds, as he sought to expand his dominion over both land and sea. His ruthless ambition led him to clash with heroes who stood against his reign, but none could match his raw might. However, hidden within the depths of his dark soul, Bane possessed a flicker of regret and a longing for redemption. As he encountered heroes who challenged his rule, they showed him the value of compassion and unity. With their guidance, Bane discovered that true power lies not in subjugation, but in protecting those in need. And so, he transformed from a tyrant to a guardian, using his'),
(12, 'https://api.duniagames.co.id/api/content/upload/file/4449410381582628110.jpg', 'Bruno', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Bruno, the Dashing Rhythm, was a charismatic and talented marksman who captivated audiences in the realm of Mobile Legends. With his flamboyant style and unparalleled precision, he became a star both on and off the battlefield. Bruno\'s journey began as a young musician, infusing his passion for music into his combat prowess. Armed with his trusty guitar and a pair of enchanted drumsticks, he unleashed a symphony of destruction upon his enemies. His swift movements and rhythmic attacks mesmerized his foes, leaving them unable to escape his relentless assault. Beyond his flashy exterior, Bruno possessed a genuine and kind-hearted nature, always striving to inspire and uplift others. He formed deep bonds with his teammates, harmonizing their strengths to create a symphony of victory. As his fame grew, Bruno used his platform to spread joy and positivity, reminding everyone that the power of music can heal wounds and bridge divides. With his dazzling performances and unwavering spirit, Bruno left an indelible mar'),
(13, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/09/MLBB_Clint.jpg', 'Clint', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Clint, the Gunslinger, was a legendary sharpshooter in the realm of Mobile Legends. With his trusty revolver and lightning-fast reflexes, he was a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. Clint\'s roots as a bounty hunter made him a master of precision and accuracy. His bullets flew true, finding their mark with deadly precision, leaving his enemies in awe of his skill. But beneath his rugged exterior, Clint possessed a sense of justice and a code of honor that guided his actions. He always fought for what was right, ensuring that the innocent were protected. Alongside his steadfast allies, Clint embarked on dangerous missions, facing overwhelming odds with unwavering determination. His quickdraws and explosive rounds turned the tide of battles, earning him respect and admiration among his peers. Clint\'s legend as a gunslinger grew, forever etching his name in the annals of Mobile Legends.'),
(14, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Mobile-Legends-Rafaela.jpg', 'Rafaela', 'Support', 'Regen & Guard', 'Roamer', 'Rafaela, the Wings of Holiness, was a divine healer who brought hope and compassion to the realm. With her angelic wings and a gentle touch, she radiated healing energy that mended wounds and restored strength. Rafaela\'s sole purpose was to bring light and comfort to those in need. Her celestial powers could not only restore her allies\' health but also protect them from harm. She floated gracefully across the battlefield, spreading love and grace in the face of darkness. Her unwavering devotion to her comrades and her selfless sacrifices inspired others to fight on with renewed vigor. Rafaela\'s healing touch became a symbol of hope, forever cementing her legacy as a beacon of light in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(15, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/cara-bermain-eudora-mobile-legends-dan-build-tersakit-2020.jpg', 'Eudora', 'Mage', 'Control & Burst', 'Mid', 'Eudora, the Lightning Sorceress, possessed a formidable mastery of lightning magic. With her powerful staff and command over thunder and lightning, she unleashed devastating spells upon her enemies. Eudora\'s raw magical power crackled and surged, engulfing her foes in electrifying fury. Her lightning bolts struck with precision, leaving her adversaries stunned and powerless. Eudora\'s quest for knowledge and power was driven by a desire to protect her loved ones and to prove her worth as a mage. Through intense study and practice, she harnessed the raw energy of storms, transforming herself into a formidable force. Eudora\'s thunderous spells echoed through the Mobile Legends realm, leaving a lasting impact and forever establishing her as a formidable sorceress.'),
(16, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/zilong-revamped-mobile-legends-project-next-uhdpaper.com-hd-5.2884.jpg', 'Zilong', 'Assassin & Fighter', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Zilong, the Son of the Dragon, hailed from a lineage of legendary warriors. Trained in the ancient arts of combat, he was destined to become a formidable force. With his swift movements and spear in hand, Zilong sought to honor his heritage by vanquishing evil and protecting the innocent. Guided by the spirit of the dragon, he traversed the battlefield with grace and unleashed a flurry of powerful strikes upon his foes. Through countless battles, Zilong honed his skills, ascending to become a true dragon among warriors. With each victory, his legend grew, inspiring others to embrace their inner strength and fight for what is right. Zilong\'s name echoed throughout the Mobile Legends realm, forever etched in history as a symbol of courage, honor, and the indomitable spirit of a dragon.'),
(17, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Mobile-Legends-Fanny.jpg', 'Fanny', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Reap', 'Jungler', 'Fanny, the High Energy Assassin, was a master of aerial acrobatics and deadly precision. With her dual blades and a grappling hook, she soared through the skies, striking fear into the hearts of her enemies. Fanny\'s agility and speed were unmatched, allowing her to swiftly eliminate her targets and escape unscathed. Her dedication to her craft and relentless pursuit of perfection made her a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. Fanny\'s name became synonymous with awe-inspiring maneuvers and unparalleled skill, forever etching her legacy as the queen of the skies in the annals of Mobile Legends.'),
(18, 'https://blog.ecnecdendshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Layla-Mobile-Legends-dengan-5-Hero-Terbaik-Ini.jpg', 'Layla', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'Layla, the Malefic Gunner, was a marksman whose skills with the rifle were unmatched. Born with a natural talent for marksmanship, she embraced her destiny as a warrior. Layla\'s attacks packed a punch, as she rained bullets upon her foes from a distance. Her resilience and determination were unwavering, propelling her to become a formidable force in battles. Despite her initial humble beginnings, Layla\'s unwavering spirit and dedication to her craft transformed her into a renowned marksman, forever remembered as the sharpshooting queen in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(19, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Mengenal-Minotaur-Hero-Mobile-Legends-Legendaris.jpeg', 'Minotaur', 'Tank & Support', 'Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Minotaur, the Son of Minos, was a fearsome tank known for his formidable strength and indomitable rage. With his massive axe and bull-like form, he commanded respect on the battlefield. Minotaur\'s anger fueled his power, and his abilities allowed him to absorb damage and control the flow of battles. Despite his savage appearance, Minotaur possessed a gentle heart, always striving to protect his allies and bring order to chaos. His unwavering loyalty and relentless determination cemented his place as a guardian and a symbol of resilience in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(20, 'https://oneesports.blob.core.windows.net/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/04/Mobile-Legends_Lolita.jpg', 'Lolita', 'Support & Tank', 'Guard & Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Lolita, the Steel Elf, was a support tank armed with a massive shield and a powerful hammer. Her primary objective was to protect her allies from harm. Lolita\'s abilities allowed her to shield her team from enemy projectiles, providing a crucial layer of defense. With her strong presence and stunning abilities, she disrupted enemy movements and turned the tide of battles. Lolita\'s unwavering commitment to her comrades and her unwavering resolve made her an irreplaceable asset, forever known as the guardian angel of the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(21, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/09/MLBB_Hayabusa-450x253.jpg', 'Hayabusa', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Hayabusa, the Shadow of Iga, was a master of the shadows and a lethal assassin. Trained in the ancient art of ninjutsu, he moved silently through the battlefield, striking his enemies with lightning speed. With his twin katanas and shadow clones, Hayabusa left no room for escape. His ability to teleport and unleash devastating combos made him a nightmare for his foes. Hayabusa\'s enigmatic nature and unparalleled skills earned him a reputation as one of the most formidable assassins in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(22, 'https://cdn.vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/stun-mobile-legend-freya.jpg', 'Freya', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Freya, the Valkyrie, was a mighty warrior known for her strength and valor. Wielding her enchanted spear, she charged into battle with unwavering determination. Freya\'s skills in combat and her ability to summon the power of the gods made her a formidable force. Her electrifying attacks and valiant spirit inspired her allies to fight alongside her, and her enemies trembled before her might. Freya\'s name became synonymous with bravery and heroism, forever remembered as a legendary warrior in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(23, 'https://www.tipspintar.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Gord-Mobile-Legends.jpg', 'Gord', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Gord, the Mystic Magician, was a powerful mage with control over the arcane arts. With his vast knowledge and an enchanted staff, he unleashed devastating spells upon his enemies. Gord\'s ability to manipulate and summon powerful cosmic energy made him a force to be reckoned with. His area-of-effect spells and explosive ultimates decimated his foes in the blink of an eye. Gord\'s mastery of magic and his insatiable hunger for knowledge placed him among the greatest spellcasters in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(24, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/03/07/1813668039.jpg', 'Natalia', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Reap', 'Jungler', 'Natalia, the Bright Claw, was a stealthy assassin who thrived in the shadows. Trained as an assassin from a young age, she struck fear into the hearts of her enemies with her twin blades. Natalia\'s unparalleled agility and ability to become invisible allowed her to infiltrate enemy lines and swiftly eliminate key targets. Her precise strikes and ability to silence opponents made her a deadly threat. Natalia\'s presence instilled terror in the hearts of her foes, forever known as the nightmare lurking in the darkness of the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(25, 'https://blue.kumparan.com/image/upload/fl_progressive,fl_lossy,c_fill,q_auto:best,w_640/v1640595158/lxjxs6gk0iptnh5dwwtf.jpg', 'Kagura', 'Mage', 'Poke & Reap', 'Mid', 'Kagura, the Onmyouji Master, was a mage who harnessed the power of the elements. With her enchanted umbrella and ancient incantations, she controlled water, lightning, and even storms. Kagura\'s graceful movements and versatile skills allowed her to deal devastating damage and manipulate the battlefield. Her ability to teleport and create powerful area-of-effect spells made her a force to be reckoned with. Kagura\'s mastery over the elements and her elegant style made her a legendary mage in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(26, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/04/13/2707615811.jpg', 'Chou', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Control', 'Exp', 'Chou, the Kung Fu Boy, was a disciplined warrior trained in the art of martial arts. With his swift punches and kicks, he delivered powerful blows to his enemies. Chou\'s agility and mobility allowed him to dodge attacks and control the battlefield. His ability to stun and disable opponents made him a formidable presence in team fights. Chou\'s unwavering determination and his dedication to his training made him a symbol of discipline and strength in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(27, 'https://media.suara.com/pictures/970x544/2021/10/16/59797-hero-tertua-mobile-legends-sun.jpg', 'Sun', 'Fighter', 'Push & Damage', 'Exp', 'Sun, the Monkey King, was a mischievous and powerful hero. With his magical staff and shape-shifting abilities, he wreaked havoc on the battlefield. Sun\'s ability to summon clones and confuse his enemies made him a versatile fighter. His ultimate, Wukong\'s Magic, allowed him to unleash devastating damage and disrupt enemy formations. Sun\'s playful nature and his cunning maneuvers made him an unpredictable force in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(28, 'https://blog.metaco.gg/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/panduan-hero-mobile-legends-alpha-featured.jpg', 'Alpha', 'Fighter', 'Charge & Damage', 'Exp', 'Alpha, the Ultimate Weapon, was a robotic warrior with devastating power. Armed with a massive sword and advanced technology, he decimated his foes with precision strikes. Alpha\'s ability to absorb damage and regenerate health made him a durable force on the battlefield. His ultimate, Force Sweep, unleashed a whirlwind of destruction, immobilizing enemies and dealing massive damage. Alpha\'s unwavering resolve and his mechanical prowess made him a fearsome presence in the Mobile Legends realm.'),
(29, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/09/16/4199840654.jpg', 'Ruby', 'Fighter & Tank', 'Crowd Control & Regen', 'Exp', 'Ruby, also known as the Little Red Hood, was not your ordinary girl. Behind her innocent appearance lay an extraordinary warrior. Armed with her trusty chains, she swung into battle with mesmerizing agility and unwavering determination. Her acrobatic prowess allowed her to effortlessly navigate the battlefield, evading attacks with remarkable grace. With every strike of her chains, Ruby immobilized her enemies, pulling them towards her and leaving them at the mercy of her relentless assaults.'),
(30, 'https://foto.kontan.co.id/fhUJiof6hoVBMFA5us0RJox8bjw=/smart/2020/10/28/176383921p.jpg', 'Yi Shun Shin', 'Assassin & Marksman', 'Reap & Chase', 'Gold', 'Yi Sun-shin, the esteemed warrior of Mobile Legends, was known for his unyielding courage and unmatched naval skills. Leading the charge on the battlefield, his presence instilled fear in the hearts of his enemies. With his trusty turtle ship and unparalleled marksmanship, Yi Sun-shin brought victory to his team time and again. His unwavering loyalty to his nation and his unwavering determination to protect his allies made him a beacon of hope in the midst of chaos. Legends whispered his name, as Yi Sun-shin\'s legend grew, forever etching his name in the annals of Mobile Legends history.'),
(31, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/04/19/1592433646.jpg', 'Moskov', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Chase', 'Gold', 'Moskov, the enigmatic and formidable marksman of Mobile Legends, possessed unparalleled skill with his trusty bow. Born with an ancient curse, he sought redemption through relentless combat. As arrows whistled through the air, each shot found its mark, obliterating his enemies with surgical precision. Moskov\'s agility and strategic prowess were unmatched, making him a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. With his piercing gaze and unyielding determination, he overcame the darkness within, proving that even in the face of adversity, true strength lies in one\'s spirit.'),
(32, 'https://vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/stun-mobile-legend-johnson.jpg', 'Johnson', 'Tank', 'Support & Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Johnson, the mighty automaton of Mobile Legends, towered over the battlefield with his imposing presence. Once a racecar champion, he was transformed into a fearsome war machine, armored and armed to protect his allies and crush his foes. Johnson\'s engines roared as he charged forward, leaving destruction in his wake. His iron fists pummeled enemies with unstoppable force, while his resilient armor absorbed their feeble attempts to halt his advance. With unwavering loyalty, Johnson shielded his teammates, turning the tides of battle with his indomitable strength. A symbol of resilience and unwavering protection, Johnson embodied the true spirit of heroism on the battlefield of Mobile Legends.'),
(33, 'https://www.ngopibareng.id/images/uploads/2022/2022-03-15/hero-cyclops-mobile-legend-sang-penyihir-bermata-satu--thumbnail-958', 'Cyclops', 'Mage', 'Poke & Control', 'Mid', 'Cyclops, the mischievous and powerful mage of Mobile Legends, danced through the battlefield with an otherworldly grace. With a single eye radiating arcane energy, he harnessed the forces of the cosmos to unleash devastating orbs upon his foes. Each flick of his wrist conjured a cataclysmic explosion, decimating enemy ranks and leaving chaos in its wake. Despite his playful demeanor, Cyclops was a force to be reckoned with, outmaneuvering his opponents with his swift movements and unpredictable spells. His ability to control the very fabric of magic made him a formidable adversary, as he weaved spells that bewildered and overwhelmed his enemies. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Cyclops was a testament to the immense power that lay within a single eye, forever etching his name in the legends of mystical might.'),
(34, 'https://asset-a.grid.id/crop/234x0:1770x957/x/photo/2019/11/26/375731137.jpg', 'Estes', 'Support', 'Regen & Guard', 'Roamer', 'Estes, the compassionate and selfless healer of Mobile Legends, emanated a soothing aura that mended wounds and restored hope on the battlefield. With a gentle touch, he mended the broken bodies of his allies, granting them renewed strength to face their enemies. Estes\' celestial powers flowed through him, casting rejuvenating spells that revitalized his team in the direst of situations. His unwavering devotion to his comrades knew no bounds as he stood at the forefront, shielding them from harm and turning the tide of battle with his benevolent presence. As the embodiment of compassion and healing, Estes proved that sometimes the greatest heroes are those who mend and nurture, forever leaving an indelible mark on the annals of Mobile Legends.'),
(35, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Bermain-Hilda-Mobile-Legends-Pelajari-Dulu-Skill-dan-Buildnya.jpg', 'Hilda', 'Fighter & Tank', 'Damage & Regen', 'Exp', 'Hilda, the fierce and indomitable warrior of Mobile Legends, roamed the battlefield like a force of nature. With her mighty axe in hand, she charged into the fray, fearless and unstoppable. Hilda\'s unwavering determination and unyielding strength made her an intimidating presence, striking fear into the hearts of her enemies. Clad in impenetrable armor, she shrugged off attacks with ease, shrugging off wounds that would fell lesser warriors. Hilda\'s connection with the wild granted her exceptional regenerative abilities, allowing her to recover swiftly and return to the fight with unwavering vigor. Her relentless pursuit of victory inspired her teammates and struck despair into the hearts of her foes. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Hilda stood as a symbol of unyielding power, forever etching her name as a legend of unstoppable might.'),
(36, 'https://storage.indoesports.com/images/hero-gg-jarang-dipakai-inilah-kelebihan-kekurangan-aurora-mobile-legends.jpg', 'Aurora', 'Mage', 'Crowd Control & Poke', 'Mid', 'Aurora, the elegant and enigmatic mage of Mobile Legends, commanded the very essence of ice and frost. With a graceful flourish of her staff, she summoned blizzards and unleashed icy tempests upon her adversaries. Aurora\'s spellbinding beauty concealed her deadly power, as she froze her enemies in their tracks with her icy abilities. The frigid winds obeyed her every whim, encasing her foes in ice prisons and leaving them vulnerable to the attacks of her allies. Her presence on the battlefield was mesmerizing, as she danced amidst the snowflakes, weaving intricate spells that left her enemies shattered and defeated. Aurora\'s icy grip struck fear into the hearts of all who dared to oppose her, forever etching her name in the legends of Mobile Legends as a mage of unparalleled elegance and power.'),
(37, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Mobile-Legends-Lapu-Lapu.jpg', 'Lapu-Lapu', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Burst', 'Exp', 'Lapu-Lapu, the fierce and honorable warrior of Mobile Legends, embodied the spirit of bravery and resilience. With his twin blades in hand, he dashed into the heat of battle, channeling the strength and determination of his ancestors. Lapu-Lapu\'s swift and precise strikes sliced through his enemies, leaving them in awe of his skill. He seamlessly switched between his dual-wielding mode, delivering devastating combos that decimated his foes. As a symbol of national pride, Lapu-Lapu drew strength from his love for his homeland, the Philippines, and fought with unwavering loyalty to protect his people. His unyielding spirit and unbreakable resolve inspired his allies, rallying them to victory in even the direst of situations. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Lapu-Lapu\'s name would forever be synonymous with bravery and unwavering courage on the battlefield.'),
(38, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vexana-ML.jpg', 'Vexana', 'Mage', 'Poke & Control', 'Mid', 'Vexana, the haunting and malevolent sorceress of Mobile Legends, emanated an aura of dark magic that instilled terror in the hearts of her enemies. With her wicked spells and cursed dolls, she manipulated the battlefield to her advantage. Vexana\'s sinister powers allowed her to control the minds of her foes, turning them against each other and sowing chaos within their ranks. Her necromantic abilities summoned ghastly spirits to aid her in battle, draining the life force of her enemies and leaving them weakened and vulnerable. With an icy stare and a malicious grin, Vexana reveled in the suffering she inflicted upon her adversaries. In the realm of Mobile Legends, her name became synonymous with darkness and treachery, forever etching her presence as a formidable and feared sorceress.'),
(39, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Roger-ML.jpg', 'Roger', 'Fighter & Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Exp', 'Roger, the ferocious and versatile hero of Mobile Legends, embodied the duality of man and beast. By day, he was a noble and skilled swordsman, and by night, he transformed into a fearsome werewolf, combining the strength and instincts of both worlds. Roger\'s agility and relentless attacks with his dual blades struck fear into the hearts of his enemies. In his werewolf form, his feral nature unleashed devastating blows that tore through his foes with savage force. With unparalleled versatility, he could swiftly switch between his human and werewolf forms, adapting to any situation on the battlefield. Roger\'s determination to protect his loved ones and his unwavering loyalty made him a formidable ally. In the realm of Mobile Legends, his name became a legend, forever etching his status as a fearsome warrior who embodied the harmonious balance between man and beast.'),
(40, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/02/23/4009726391.png', 'Karrie', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'Karrie, the agile and relentless marksman of Mobile Legends, was a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. With her dual light blades, she danced through the chaos, striking her enemies with incredible speed and precision. Karrie\'s passive ability allowed her to penetrate enemy defenses, shredding their armor and dealing massive damage. Her mobility and evasiveness made her a difficult target to catch, as she weaved through the battlefield, effortlessly kiting her opponents. With each shot, she unleashed the full power of her determination and skill, melting away the health bars of her foes. Karrie\'s unmatched ability to unleash a storm of projectiles made her a nightmare for tanks and squishy targets alike. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Karrie\'s name became synonymous with swift and deadly marksmanship, forever etching her place as an icon of precision and relentless firepower.'),
(41, 'https://akcdn.detik.net.id/visual/2017/07/21/cc443629-3f8f-4609-a936-b8506d00e996_169.jpg?w=650', 'Gatotkaca', 'Tank & Fighter', 'Crowd Control & Burst', 'Exp', 'Gatotkaca, the indomitable tank of Mobile Legends, stood as an immovable fortress on the battlefield. With his colossal strength and unyielding determination, he protected his allies and punished his enemies. Gatotkaca\'s massive shield absorbed incoming damage, while his devastating abilities unleashed havoc upon his foes. With a mighty leap, he crashed into the midst of battle, stunning his enemies and disrupting their formations. His signature ultimate ability, Avatar of Guardian, transformed him into an unstoppable force, rendering him immune to crowd control and allowing him to unleash devastating area-of-effect damage. Gatotkaca\'s unwavering loyalty to justice and his unbreakable spirit inspired his teammates, rallying them to victory. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Gatotkaca\'s name became synonymous with unyielding defense and unwavering bravery, forever etching his place as a true guardian of the battlefield.'),
(42, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Hero-Harley-Cover-696x464.jpg', 'Harley', 'Mage & Assassin', 'Burst & Poke', 'Jungler', 'Harley, the mischievous and cunning mage of Mobile Legends, wielded his enchanted cards with deadly precision. With a sly grin and a flick of his wrist, he unleashed arcane projectiles that danced through the air, seeking out his foes with unerring accuracy. Harley\'s mobility was unmatched as he blinked through the battlefield, leaving behind a trail of magic that exploded upon contact, causing chaos and confusion among his enemies. His cunning nature allowed him to manipulate the flow of battle, creating opportunities for his team to strike. With his ultimate ability, Space Escape, he vanished into thin air, reappearing with a burst of magical energy, catching his enemies off guard. Harley\'s playful personality and sharp intellect made him a formidable adversary, forever keeping his enemies on their toes. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Harley\'s name became synonymous with trickery and devastating magical prowess, forever etching his place as a master of arcane deception.'),
(43, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Irithel.jpg', 'Irithel', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Irithel, the graceful and deadly ranger of Mobile Legends, danced through the battlefield with elegance and precision. With her enchanted crossbow, she unleashed a barrage of arrows upon her enemies, each shot finding its mark with lethal accuracy. Irithel\'s unique ability allowed her to move while attacking, making her a mobile powerhouse on the battlefield. Her ultimate ability, Heavy Crossbow, transformed her attacks into a flurry of devastating bolts, shredding through enemy defenses with ease. With her trusty tiger companion, Leo, by her side, Irithel had a loyal ally that added an extra layer of danger to her attacks. As a ranged powerhouse, she was capable of decimating enemies from a safe distance, while her agility allowed her to swiftly dodge incoming threats. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Irithel\'s name became synonymous with deadly precision and unmatched grace, forever etching her place as a fearsome ranger of unparalleled skill.'),
(44, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Hero-Grock-Wallpaper.jpg', 'Grock', 'Tank', 'Crowd Control & Initiator', 'Roamer', 'Grock, the mighty and indomitable tank of Mobile Legends, towered over the battlefield like a living mountain. With his massive stone fists and impenetrable armor, he embodied the very essence of strength and resilience. Grock\'s passive ability, Living Wall, allowed him to create barriers out of the terrain, providing himself and his allies with extra protection. He charged into battle, using his powerful abilities to stun and disrupt his enemies, leaving them vulnerable to the onslaught of his team. Grock\'s ultimate ability, Wild Charge, enabled him to dash forward with tremendous force, dealing damage and knocking back enemies in his path. His presence alone commanded respect, as he defended his teammates with unwavering loyalty. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Grock\'s name became synonymous with unbreakable defense and unwavering determination, forever etching his place as a guardian of the battlefield.'),
(45, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Argus-ML.jpg', 'Argus', 'Fighter', 'Charge & Burst', 'Exp', 'Argus, the relentless and vengeful warrior of Mobile Legends, emerged from the depths of darkness with a burning desire for redemption. Clad in ancient armor and wielding his mighty demonic blade, he struck fear into the hearts of his enemies. Argus\' passive ability, Warmonger, allowed him to enter a powered state, enhancing his attacks and granting him increased durability. With his ultimate ability, Eternal Evil, he transformed into an unstoppable force, becoming immune to crowd control and gaining enhanced damage output. Argus relentlessly pursued his foes, striking them down with swift and devastating slashes. His thirst for revenge fueled his every move, as he sought to eradicate evil from the realm. Though his powers came with a price, his unwavering determination and unparalleled strength made him a formidable adversary. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Argus\' name became synonymous with vengeance and unrelenting fury, forever etching his place as a warrior driven by a burning desire for justice.'),
(46, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/09/MLBB_Odette-450x253.jpg', 'Odette', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Odette, the enchanting and ethereal mage of Mobile Legends, graced the battlefield with her mesmerizing presence. With her mastery of water magic, she conjured magnificent spells that swept across the battlefield with grace and beauty. Odette\'s abilities flowed like a cascading river, entrapping her enemies in swirling currents and unleashing devastating torrents of water. Her ultimate ability, Swan Song, summoned a flock of powerful swans that unleashed a flurry of magical projectiles, dealing immense damage to all in their path. As a mage, Odette excelled at controlling the flow of battle, immobilizing and stunning her foes with her aquatic abilities. Her elegance and poise mirrored her deadly powers, making her a force to be reckoned with. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Odette\'s name became synonymous with grace and destructive beauty, forever etching her place as a mage of unparalleled enchantment.'),
(47, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/09/MLBB_Lancelot-450x253.jpg', 'Lancelot', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Lancelot, the agile and dashing assassin of Mobile Legends, moved through the battlefield with unparalleled grace and precision. With his dual blades, he struck fear into the hearts of his enemies as he danced through their defenses, leaving a trail of devastation in his wake. Lancelot\'s swift and deadly attacks allowed him to quickly eliminate his targets before they even had a chance to react. His evasive nature and swift movement made him a slippery adversary, often appearing and disappearing in the blink of an eye. With his ultimate ability, Phantom Execution, Lancelot dashed through his enemies, dealing multiple strikes of deadly damage. His unparalleled skill in the art of swordplay and his unwavering determination to uphold justice made him a formidable force on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Lancelot\'s name became synonymous with precision and lethal finesse, forever etching his place as an assassin of unmatched elegance and deadly prowess.'),
(48, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Diggie-ML.jpg', 'Diggie', 'Support', 'Guard & Poke', 'Roamer', 'Diggie, the quirky and ingenious support hero of Mobile Legends, hatched onto the battlefield with his mechanical contraptions and boundless enthusiasm. With his trusty clockwork companion, Diggie scurried around, providing invaluable support to his allies. His abilities were a testament to his inventive nature, as he healed and protected his teammates with ingenious gadgets and traps. Diggie\'s ultimate ability, Time Journey, allowed him to turn back time and revive fallen allies, turning the tide of battle in his team\'s favor. His disruptive abilities, such as his ability to stun enemies and disrupt their skills, made him a nuisance to his foes. Despite his small size, Diggie\'s impact on the battlefield was immeasurable, as he selflessly dedicated himself to the well-being of his team. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Diggie\'s name became synonymous with innovation and unwavering support, forever etching his place as a hero whose brilliance shone through his mechanical ingenuity.'),
(49, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/03/22/1676298367.jpg', 'Hylos', 'Tank', 'Guard & Initiator', 'Roamer', 'Hylos, the towering and resilient tank of Mobile Legends, commanded the power of nature itself. With his enormous strength and unyielding determination, he became an immovable force on the battlefield. Hylos\' abilities were imbued with the essence of the earth, allowing him to manipulate the terrain and control the flow of battle. With his ultimate ability, Glorious Pathway, he created a path of thorns that damaged and slowed enemies while providing movement speed to his allies. Hylos\' passive ability, Thickened Blood, allowed him to regenerate health based on his maximum mana, making him a formidable tank to bring down. With his sturdy build and protective nature, he shielded his teammates from harm, absorbing damage with ease. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Hylos\' name became synonymous with unbreakable defense and unwavering strength, forever etching his place as a guardian of nature and a pillar of resilience on the battlefield.'),
(50, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Mobile-Legends-Zhask.jpg', 'Zhask', 'Mage', 'Chase & Damage', 'Mid', 'Zhask, the master of the abyss and fearsome mage of Mobile Legends, commanded a legion of deadly creatures. With his incredible control over dark energy, Zhask summoned and controlled the deadly Nightmaric Spawn, unleashing them upon his enemies. Zhask\'s presence on the battlefield was a constant reminder of the terror that awaited his foes. His ultimate ability, Dominator\'s Descent, transformed him into an immobile turret while his Spawn ravaged his enemies, dealing devastating damage. Zhask\'s relentless onslaught of dark magic overwhelmed his adversaries, leaving them helpless against the abyssal forces at his command. With each victory, he grew stronger, channeling the powers of darkness into his attacks. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Zhask\'s name became synonymous with unbridled power and the merciless dominance of the abyss, forever etching his place as a mage of unparalleled darkness and destruction.'),
(51, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/sites/2/2022/02/MLBB_IceSchyteHelcurt.jpg', 'Helcurt', 'Assassin', 'Push & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Helcurt, the shadowy and elusive assassin of Mobile Legends, emerged from the darkness to strike fear into the hearts of his enemies. With his wickedly sharp twin blades and his mastery over shadows, Helcurt was a relentless hunter who specialized in ambushing his targets. Born blind, his other senses were heightened to a supernatural degree, allowing him to perceive the world around him with unparalleled precision. Helcurt\'s passive ability, Race Advantage, made him immune to vision-reliant skills and allowed him to strike swiftly and silently. With his ultimate ability, Deadly Stinger, he plunged the battlefield into darkness, silencing and disorienting his foes, leaving them vulnerable to his deadly assaults. Helcurt\'s agility and burst damage made him a fearsome assassin, capable of eliminating high-priority targets in the blink of an eye. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Helcurt\'s name became synonymous with darkness and lethal precision, forever etching his place as a master of shadow and a nightmare to '),
(52, 'https://cdn.vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Pharsa-oke.png', 'Pharsa', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Pharsa, the majestic and ethereal mage of Mobile Legends, soared through the skies, raining down destruction upon her enemies. With her avian form and powerful wings, Pharsa commanded the very elements of wind and lightning. Her abilities channeled the fury of storms, allowing her to unleash devastating magic upon her foes from a safe distance. Pharsa\'s ultimate ability, Feathered Air Strike, called upon a barrage of feathered arrows that pierced through multiple enemies, dealing massive area-of-effect damage. Her strategic positioning and long-range attacks made her a formidable presence on the battlefield, as she could rain down destruction from afar while remaining elusive. Pharsa\'s dominion over the skies instilled fear in her enemies, as they were constantly under threat of her thunderous assaults. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Pharsa\'s name became synonymous with the might of storms and the elegance of flight, forever etching her place as a mage of unrivaled aerial supremacy.');
INSERT INTO `heroes` (`id`, `images`, `names`, `roles`, `specialities`, `lane`, `desc`) VALUES
(53, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Lesley.jpg', 'Lesley', 'Assassin & Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Lesley, the deadly and precise sniper of Mobile Legends, embodied the essence of stealth and precision. With her dual pistols and impeccable aim, she struck fear into the hearts of her enemies from a distance. Lesley\'s passive ability, Lethal Shot, allowed her to deal extra damage to enemies with low health, ensuring that no target could escape her sight. With her ultimate ability, Ultimate Snipe, she locked onto her target and unleashed a powerful shot that pierced through multiple enemies, delivering devastating damage. Lesley\'s agility and quick reflexes allowed her to reposition herself swiftly, making her a difficult target to pin down. Her ability to scout the battlefield with her S.A.B.E.R. reconnaissance drone provided valuable information to her team, granting them a strategic advantage. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Lesley\'s name became synonymous with deadly precision and unrivaled marksmanship, forever etching her place as a sniper whose bullets found their mark with lethal accuracy.'),
(54, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Mobile-Legends-Jawhead.jpg', 'Jawhead', 'Fighter', 'Charge & Burst', 'Exp', 'Jawhead, the brawny and rebellious fighter of Mobile Legends, was a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. With his powerful mechanical arms and indomitable strength, Jawhead unleashed devastating blows upon his enemies. His grappling hook allowed him to initiate fights and pull enemies towards him, leaving them vulnerable to his ferocious attacks. Jawhead\'s ultimate ability, Ejector, allowed him to grab an enemy and hurl them towards his team, turning the tide of battle in their favor. His resilience and tenacity made him a formidable frontline presence, soaking up damage and disrupting enemy formations. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Jawhead\'s name became synonymous with raw power and an unyielding spirit, forever etching his place as a fighter whose punches echoed with unmatched force.'),
(55, 'https://c.inilah.com/2023/01/0118_023119_c512_inilah.com_.jpg', 'Angela', 'Support', 'Guard & Support', 'Roamer', 'Angela, the compassionate and supportive hero of Mobile Legends, provided unwavering aid to her allies on the battlefield. With her healing abilities and protective spells, Angela became a beacon of hope in the midst of chaos. Her ultimate ability, Heartguard, allowed her to link with an ally, providing them with a shield and continuous healing, strengthening their resilience and allowing them to face their foes with renewed vigor. Angela\'s mobility and crowd control abilities made her a versatile support, capable of saving teammates from certain demise or disrupting enemy advances. Her selflessness and dedication to the well-being of her team made her a beloved ally on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Angela\'s name became synonymous with unwavering support and boundless compassion, forever etching her place as a guardian angel who watched over her allies with unwavering devotion.'),
(56, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Gusion-ML.jpg', 'Gusion', 'Assassin', 'Magic Damage & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Gusion, the agile and deadly mage assassin of Mobile Legends, danced through the battlefield with grace and precision. With his dual daggers and mastery over magic, Gusion struck fear into the hearts of his enemies. His rapid and devastating combo attacks allowed him to swiftly eliminate his targets before they could even react. Gusion\'s ultimate ability, Incandescence, teleported him to a target location, dealing significant damage to all enemies within the area. His mobility and burst damage made him a formidable assassin, capable of swiftly eliminating high-priority targets. Gusion\'s relentless pursuit of perfection in his craft earned him a reputation as a master of magic and blade. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Gusion\'s name became synonymous with swift destruction and unparalleled elegance, forever etching his place as a mage assassin whose every strike was a deadly work of art.'),
(57, 'https://asset-a.grid.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2019/09/13/3807962576.jpg', 'Valir', 'Mage', 'Damage & Guard', 'Mid', 'Valir, the fiery and versatile mage of Mobile Legends, harnessed the power of flames to incinerate his enemies. With his pyrokinetic abilities, Valir commanded the very essence of fire, unleashing devastating spells upon his foes. His ultimate ability, Vengeance Flame, engulfed the battlefield in flames, dealing continuous damage to enemies within the area. Valir\'s crowd control abilities, such as his ability to stun and knock back enemies, allowed him to control the flow of battle, disrupting his opponents\' strategies. With his versatility and area-of-effect damage, Valir excelled at team fights and sieges. His fiery presence inspired fear and respect, as he burned his enemies to ashes. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Valir\'s name became synonymous with the inferno\'s wrath and the scorching power of fire, forever etching his place as a mage whose flames consumed all who stood against him.'),
(58, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/08/MLBB_Martis.jpg', 'Martis', 'Fighter', 'Reap & Charge', 'Exp', 'Martis, the relentless and ferocious fighter of Mobile Legends, charged into battle with unwavering determination. With his mighty axe and superior strength, Martis cleaved through his enemies with brutal force. His ability to engage and disrupt his opponents made him a formidable presence on the battlefield. Martis\' ultimate ability, Mortal Coil, allowed him to pull enemies towards him, setting them up for devastating combos. His passive ability, Ashura Aura, enhanced his attacks and granted him increased lifesteal, allowing him to sustain in prolonged fights. Martis\' resilience and unyielding spirit made him a force to be reckoned with, as he fought relentlessly for victory. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Martis\' name became synonymous with relentless pursuit and unrelenting aggression, forever etching his place as a fighter whose battle cry shook the very foundations of the battlefield.'),
(59, 'https://assets.pikiran-rakyat.com/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/02/05/1422563520.png', 'Uranus', 'Tank', 'Regen', 'Exp', 'Uranus, the celestial and durable tank of Mobile Legends, radiated with cosmic energy as he stepped onto the battlefield. With his celestial powers, Uranus absorbed and redirected damage, making him an incredibly resilient tank. His ultimate ability, Consecration, created an aura of healing that regenerated his health and that of nearby allies. Uranus\' ability to sustain in team fights and provide support to his team made him an invaluable asset on the front lines. His passive ability, Radiance, granted him increased HP regeneration, further enhancing his durability. Uranus\' steadfast presence and unwavering determination inspired his allies, as he stood as a protector against all threats. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Uranus\' name became synonymous with celestial resilience and unwavering protection, forever etching his place as a tank whose cosmic energy shielded his teammates from harm.'),
(60, 'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEipkd9jdbNM_diKiMuMn4UH-pN5FPmAI2RcyypYQN61KypZgt8AHzFtMtAlWLofyux3KHvkhtcVJstct1h_iYBeJd6eew3VD-Bvv7YyTqyzn1QZt5Hpwy5mnEoprkUhEf6CVH7CepJJzNZwY8RRkbAQ62pNhphy_m3AoZP60ZITxDPLbJfVvbDDgU23tg/s1600/Hanabi%20Revamp%202022,%20Apakah%20Layak%20Jadi%20Marksman%20Meta%20-%20AdityaTekno.jpg', 'Hanabi', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'Hanabi, the deadly and agile marksman of Mobile Legends, unleashed a storm of arrows upon her enemies. With her elegant bow and exceptional marksmanship, Hanabi dominated the battlefield with her relentless barrage of projectiles. Her passive ability, Ninjutsu: Soul Scroll, allowed her to store energy with each basic attack, increasing her damage output. Hanabi\'s ultimate ability, Higanbana, unleashed a rain of arrows that pierced through multiple enemies, dealing devastating damage. Her ability to reposition herself swiftly and her enhanced basic attacks made her a formidable marksman capable of quickly eliminating her targets. Hanabi\'s determination and precision with her bow made her a force to be reckoned with. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Hanabi\'s name became synonymous with lethal accuracy and unyielding focus, forever etching her place as a marksman whose arrows found their mark with deadly precision.'),
(61, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Hero-Change-Cover.jpg', 'Chang\'e', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Chang\'e, the graceful and mystical mage of Mobile Legends, wove intricate spells that mesmerized and overwhelmed her enemies. With her celestial powers and her mastery of lunar magic, Chang\'e controlled the very forces of nature. Her ultimate ability, Meteor Shower, summoned a barrage of falling stars that rained down upon her foes, dealing massive area-of-effect damage. Chang\'e\'s passive ability, Harmony, allowed her to accumulate energy and enhance her skills, granting her increased spell vamp. Her crowd control abilities, such as her ability to stun and slow enemies, allowed her to dictate the flow of battle. Chang\'e\'s elegance and otherworldly presence made her a captivating mage, capable of turning the tide of battle with a flick of her wrist. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Chang\'e\'s name became synonymous with celestial beauty and devastating magic, forever etching her place as a mage whose spells danced with the grace of the moon.'),
(62, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/kaja-hero-op-gak-laku-scaled.jpg', 'Kaja', 'Fighter & Support', 'Control & Charge', 'Exp', 'Kaja, the majestic and commanding support hero of Mobile Legends, descended upon the battlefield with divine power. With his electrifying whip and sacred abilities, Kaja controlled the flow of battle and protected his allies. His ultimate ability, Divine Judgment, allowed him to seize an enemy hero and bring them into his team, rendering them helpless and vulnerable to focused attacks. Kaja\'s crowd control abilities, such as his ability to stun and knock up enemies, made him a formidable disruptor. With his passive ability, Eye of the Storm, he enhanced his basic attacks, dealing additional magic damage and regenerating his own health. Kaja\'s unwavering dedication to justice and his team made him an exceptional support hero, ensuring his allies\' safety and securing victory. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Kaja\'s name became synonymous with divine intervention and unwavering loyalty, forever etching his place as a support hero whose presence turned the tide of battle.'),
(63, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Selena-ML.jpg', 'Selena', 'Mage & Assassin', 'Initiator & Reap', 'Jungler', 'Selena, the enigmatic and deadly mage-assassin of Mobile Legends, stalked her prey from the shadows. With her dual form and mastery of dark and light magic, Selena struck fear into the hearts of her enemies. Her ability to seamlessly switch between her human and abyssal forms gave her unparalleled versatility and allowed her to adapt to different situations. Selena\'s ultimate ability, Abyssal Trap, laid deadly traps that immobilized and dealt damage to unsuspecting foes. Her exceptional burst damage and crowd control abilities made her a lethal assassin, capable of quickly eliminating high-priority targets. Selena\'s shadowy presence and mastery of the arcane arts made her a feared adversary. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Selena\'s name became synonymous with darkness and cunning, forever etching her place as a mage-assassin whose strikes emerged from the depths of shadow and left her enemies in eternal darkness.'),
(64, 'https://blue.kumparan.com/image/upload/v1634025439/01g8sjnnrbvbwxmy2acj4adq4w.jpg', 'Aldous', 'Fighter', 'Support & Burst', 'Exp', 'Aldous, the mighty and indomitable fighter of Mobile Legends, wielded the power of the Abyssal Traps to vanquish his enemies. With his colossal hammer and unstoppable strength, Aldous struck fear into the hearts of his foes. His passive ability, Contract: Chase Fate, allowed him to stack damage with each enemy minion and hero he eliminated, exponentially increasing his attack power. Aldous\' ultimate ability, Contract: Explosion, unleashed a devastating blow that dealt massive damage to a single target, making him a formidable duelist. His resilience and ability to absorb damage made him a daunting presence on the battlefield. Aldous\' unwavering determination and commitment to his cause made him a symbol of unyielding power. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Aldous\' name became synonymous with raw strength and unbreakable resolve, forever etching his place as a fighter whose strikes shook the very foundations of the battlefield.'),
(65, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Mengenal-Claude-Mobile-Legend-dan-Cara-Menggunakannya.jpg', 'Claude', 'Marksman', 'Chase & Burst', 'Gold', 'Claude, the agile and elusive marksman of Mobile Legends, danced through the battlefield with unparalleled finesse. With his twin guns and masterful thieving skills, Claude left his enemies in awe of his swift and deadly attacks. His passive ability, Battle Mirror Image, allowed him to create clones that dealt additional damage and absorbed enemy attacks. Claude\'s ultimate ability, Blazing Duet, fired a barrage of bullets that pierced through enemies, dealing devastating damage. His ability to quickly dash around the battlefield and his enhanced basic attacks made him a formidable marksman capable of swiftly eliminating his targets. Claude\'s charm and charisma, combined with his unparalleled thieving skills, made him a legend in the realm of Mobile Legends. His name became synonymous with calculated precision and daring exploits, forever etching his place as a marksman whose every shot was a work of art.'),
(66, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/05/22/1196905753.jpg', 'Vale', 'Mage', 'Crowd Control & Burst', 'Mid', 'Vale, the mystical and enigmatic mage of Mobile Legends, commanded the forces of nature with grace and elegance. With his magical staff and control over wind and lightning, Vale unleashed devastating spells upon his enemies. His ultimate ability, Windstorm, created a tempest that damaged and slowed enemies within its radius. Vale\'s crowd control abilities, such as his ability to immobilize and knock back enemies, allowed him to manipulate the battlefield and disrupt his opponents\' strategies. His passive ability, Windtalk, enhanced his movement speed and provided him with extra magic damage on his next attack. Vale\'s ethereal presence and connection to nature made him a captivating mage, capable of turning the tides of battle with the might of the elements. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Vale\'s name became synonymous with arcane elegance and elemental mastery, forever etching his place as a mage whose spells danced with the power of the wind and lightning.'),
(67, 'https://api.duniagames.co.id/api/content/upload/file/3721993641657121228.jpg', 'Leomord', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Burst', 'Exp', 'Leomord, the fearless and relentless fighter of Mobile Legends, rode into battle atop his mighty steed, Barbiel. With his massive lance and unwavering courage, Leomord charged headlong into the fray. His ultimate ability, Phantom Steed, transformed him into a mounted knight, granting him enhanced mobility and increased damage. Leomord\'s passive ability, Decimation, allowed him to strike multiple enemies with his basic attacks, dealing bonus damage. His ability to dive into the heart of battle and disrupt enemy formations made him a formidable force on the battlefield. Leomord\'s unwavering loyalty and determination to protect his kingdom made him a symbol of honor and chivalry. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Leomord\'s name became synonymous with noble valor and unmatched strength, forever etching his place as a fighter whose mounted charges struck fear into the hearts of his enemies.'),
(68, 'https://oneesports.azureedge.net/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/05/MLBB_Lunox-1-1024x639.jpg', 'Lunox', 'Mage', 'Damage & Burst', 'Mid', 'Lunox, the enigmatic and powerful mage of Mobile Legends, balanced the forces of light and dark with extraordinary prowess. With her dual personalities, Lunox unleashed devastating spells upon her enemies. Her ultimate ability, Chaos Assault, allowed her to teleport and deal damage to nearby enemies. Lunox\'s unique mechanic of switching between her Order and Chaos forms granted her versatility in combat. In her Order form, she excelled at crowd control and healing, while in her Chaos form, she unleashed destructive bursts of magic damage. Her ability to manipulate the balance between light and dark made her a formidable mage capable of turning the tide of battle. Lunox\'s mysterious aura and her mastery over opposing forces made her an unparalleled mage. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Lunox\'s name became synonymous with duality and otherworldly power, forever etching her place as a mage whose spells defied comprehension.'),
(69, 'https://vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Hanzo-MLBB.jpeg', 'Hanzo', 'Assassin', 'Poke & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Hanzo, the swift and deadly ninja assassin of Mobile Legends, moved through the shadows with deadly precision. With his cursed spirits and swift strikes, Hanzo instilled fear in the hearts of his enemies. His ultimate ability, Phantom Shuriken, allowed him to throw multiple shurikens at his target, dealing significant damage. Hanzo\'s passive ability, Ninjutsu: Devastator, empowered his basic attacks, allowing him to drain his enemies\' energy and deal additional damage. His ability to traverse through walls and ambush unsuspecting foes made him an unpredictable and lethal assassin. Hanzo\'s unwavering dedication to his ninja training and his thirst for vengeance made him a fearsome adversary. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Hanzo\'s name became synonymous with shadows and swift retribution, forever etching his place as an assassin whose strikes struck from the darkness with lethal precision.'),
(70, 'https://esports.id/img/article/844820200708095327.jpg', 'Belerick', 'Tank', 'Crowd Control & Regen', 'Roamer', 'Belerick, the steadfast and resilient tank of Mobile Legends, stood as a guardian of nature on the battlefield. With his ancient tree trunk and regenerative abilities, Belerick protected his allies and absorbed enemy damage. His ultimate ability, Nature\'s Shield, created a protective barrier that mitigated incoming damage and restored health to himself and nearby allies. Belerick\'s passive ability, Divine Fervor, granted him increased HP regeneration and enhanced his basic attacks, dealing additional magic damage. His ability to initiate team fights and provide sustained support made him a formidable tank. Belerick\'s unwavering commitment to preserving the balance of nature and his selfless devotion to his allies made him a true protector. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Belerick\'s name became synonymous with natural resilience and unwavering defense, forever etching his place as a tank whose roots dug deep and shielded his comrades from harm.'),
(71, 'https://img.esportsku.com/wp-content/uploads//2020/02/kimmy-1200x752.png', 'Kimmy', 'Marksman & Mage', 'Damage & Magic Damage', 'Gold', 'Kimmy, the energetic and high-tech marksman of Mobile Legends, unleashed a barrage of bullets and energy blasts upon her enemies. With her powerful arm-mounted gun and advanced weaponry, Kimmy brought a futuristic flair to the battlefield. Her unique mechanic allowed her to simultaneously move and attack, giving her unmatched mobility and continuous damage output. Kimmy\'s ultimate ability, Energy Transformation, transformed her basic attacks into long-range energy blasts, dealing significant damage to enemies within her line of fire. Her ability to kite enemies and harass from a distance made her a formidable marksman. Kimmy\'s bubbly personality and cutting-edge technology made her a fan favorite, as she danced through the battlefield with unmatched agility. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Kimmy\'s name became synonymous with futuristic firepower and relentless energy, forever etching her place as a marksman whose bullets lit up the battlefield.'),
(72, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/sites/2/2022/05/thamuz-mobile-legends-moonton.jpg', 'Thamuz', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Thamuz, the fiery and relentless warrior of Mobile Legends, wielded dual scythes and embraced the power of flames. With his devastating attacks and fire-based abilities, Thamuz wreaked havoc upon his enemies. His ultimate ability, Cauterant Inferno, engulfed his scythes in flames, enhancing his attacks and dealing area-of-effect damage. Thamuz\'s passive ability, King\'s Calling, granted him enhanced lifesteal and increased damage against enemy heroes. His ability to dive into the heart of battle and sustain through damage made him a formidable fighter. Thamuz\'s fiery presence and his affinity for flames made him a fearsome adversary. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Thamuz\'s name became synonymous with blazing fury and unyielding strength, forever etching his place as a warrior whose scythes carved a path of destruction.'),
(73, 'https://img.esportsku.com/wp-content/uploads//2019/09/Harith.jpg', 'Harith', 'Mage', 'Chase & Damage', 'Mid', 'Harith, the agile and elusive mage of Mobile Legends, manipulated time and space to outmaneuver his opponents. With his magical staff and mastery over chrono energy, Harith controlled the flow of battle with his teleportation abilities. His ultimate ability, Zaman Force, created a temporal rift that transported him back in time, restoring his health and mana while dealing damage to nearby enemies. Harith\'s passive ability, Key Insight, granted him increased movement speed and reduced cooldowns, allowing him to cast spells with incredible frequency. His ability to dash around the battlefield and unleash devastating bursts of magic damage made him a formidable mage. Harith\'s whimsical personality and his mastery over chrono magic made him a beloved hero among Mobile Legends players. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Harith\'s name became synonymous with temporal manipulation and unmatched agility, forever etching his place as a mage whose spells defied the constraints of time.'),
(74, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/2023/03/MLBB_Minsitthar_revamp.webp', 'Minsitthar', 'Fighter & Support', 'Initiator & Crowd Control', 'Exp', 'Minsitthar, the valiant and resolute warrior of Mobile Legends, commanded the battlefield with his powerful lance and iron will. With his ultimate ability, King\'s Calling, Minsitthar pulled enemies towards him and suppressed their abilities, rendering them helpless and vulnerable to his team\'s attacks. Minsitthar\'s passive ability, Lord\'s Ambition, enhanced his basic attacks, granting him additional damage and a chance to reduce enemy movement speed. His ability to initiate team fights and disrupt enemy formations made him a formidable tank and crowd control specialist. Minsitthar\'s unwavering loyalty to his kingdom and his determination to protect his allies made him a true leader on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Minsitthar\'s name became synonymous with royal authority and unyielding strength, forever etching his place as a warrior whose banner rallied his allies to victory.'),
(75, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/07/15/2164141579.jpg', 'Kadita', 'Mage & Assassin', 'Charge & Burst', 'Mid', 'Kadita, the mesmerizing and elusive mage-assassin of Mobile Legends, ruled the depths of the sea with her tidal powers. With her trident and aquatic abilities, Kadita unleashed devastating watery attacks upon her enemies. Her ultimate ability, Rough Waves, created a massive whirlpool that damaged and pulled in enemies, leaving them vulnerable to her subsequent attacks. Kadita\'s passive ability, Thalassic Blessing, enhanced her mobility and granted her additional magic damage on her next attack. Her ability to swiftly dash through the battlefield and unleash lethal bursts of magic damage made her a formidable assassin. Kadita\'s ethereal beauty and her connection to the sea made her a captivating hero, as she danced through the waves with lethal grace. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Kadita\'s name became synonymous with aquatic elegance and deadly precision, forever etching her place as a mage-assassin whose tidal powers overwhelmed her enemies.'),
(76, 'https://img.okezone.com/content/2022/07/09/326/2626768/panduan-skill-baru-dan-combo-faramis-di-mobile-legends-491Ri2qBox.jpg', 'Faramis', 'Support & Mage', 'Guard & Charge', 'Roamer', 'Faramis, the spectral and mystical support mage of Mobile Legends, commanded an army of ghosts to aid his allies and haunt his enemies. With his haunting abilities and ethereal presence, Faramis turned the tide of battle in his team\'s favor. His ultimate ability, Ghost Burden, resurrected fallen allies as ghosts, allowing them to continue fighting and dealing damage to enemies. Faramis\' passive ability, Vicious Retrieval, restored his health and mana upon eliminating enemy heroes, ensuring his sustainability in prolonged engagements. His ability to heal, resurrect, and provide crowd control made him a valuable asset to any team. Faramis\' enigmatic nature and his connection to the realm of spirits made him a captivating and mysterious hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Faramis\' name became synonymous with spectral guidance and unwavering loyalty, forever etching his place as a support mage whose presence transcended death.'),
(77, 'https://blue.kumparan.com/image/upload/fl_progressive,fl_lossy,c_fill,q_auto:best,w_640/v1624954328/fqa8f4mh9a9a000rkfpv.jpg', 'Badang', 'Fighter', 'Charge & Burst', 'Exp', 'Badang, the powerful and relentless fighter of Mobile Legends, unleashed devastating blows upon his enemies with his mighty fists. With his incredible strength and martial arts prowess, Badang shattered the battlefield with his powerful abilities. His ultimate ability, Fist Crack, dealt massive area-of-effect damage and knocked enemies into the air. Badang\'s passive ability, Qigong Fist, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and stun enemies. His ability to engage in close combat and deliver devastating combos made him a formidable fighter. Badang\'s unyielding determination and his mastery of martial arts made him a force to be reckoned with. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Badang\'s name became synonymous with raw power and unwavering resilience, forever etching his place as a fighter whose fists struck with unrelenting force.'),
(78, 'https://cdn.vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/khufra-ml-1a.jpg', 'Khufra', 'Tank & Support', 'Initiator & Crowd Control', 'Roamer', 'Khufra, the hulking and tenacious tank of Mobile Legends, dominated the battlefield with his massive chain and formidable defensive capabilities. With his ultimate ability, Tyrant\'s Rage, Khufra lunged forward, stunning enemies in his path and disrupting their movements. Khufra\'s passive ability, Spell Curse, reduced the effectiveness of enemy healing and increased his own HP regeneration. His ability to initiate team fights, absorb damage, and crowd control enemies made him a cornerstone of any team composition. Khufra\'s unwavering loyalty to his kingdom and his dedication to maintaining order made him a revered and respected hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Khufra\'s name became synonymous with unwavering defense and unbreakable resolve, forever etching his place as a tank whose chains shackled his enemies and shielded his allies.'),
(79, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Granger-ML.jpg', 'Granger', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Granger, the charismatic and skilled marksman of Mobile Legends, wielded his twin revolvers with deadly accuracy. With his impeccable aim and powerful bullets, Granger eliminated his enemies with style and finesse. His ultimate ability, Death Sonata, unleashed a barrage of bullets that pierced through multiple enemies, dealing devastating damage. Granger\'s passive ability, Caprice, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and reduce enemy movement speed. His ability to quickly burst down enemies and dash around the battlefield made him a formidable marksman. Granger\'s charming personality and his impeccable marksmanship made him a fan favorite, as he left a trail of defeated foes in his wake. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Granger\'s name became synonymous with stylish precision and unmatched flair, forever etching his place as a marksman whose bullets painted the battlefield in a symphony of destruction.'),
(80, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Mobile-Legends-Guinevere.jpg', 'Guinevere', 'Fighter', 'Magic Damage & Burst', 'Exp', 'Guinevere, the elegant and agile mage-fighter of Mobile Legends, danced through the battlefield with grace and lethal precision. With her enchanted sword and magical abilities, Guinevere unleashed devastating combos upon her enemies. Her ultimate ability, Violet Requiem, dashed forward and unleashed a whirlwind of energy, damaging and stunning enemies caught in its path. Guinevere\'s passive ability, Magic Thump, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal additional magic damage and reduce enemy movement speed. Her ability to engage in close combat, deal burst damage, and provide crowd control made her a formidable force. Guinevere\'s enchanting presence and her mastery of both swordsmanship and magic made her a captivating hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Guinevere\'s name became synonymous with elegance and lethal grace, forever etching her place as a mage-fighter whose every strike was a work of art.'),
(81, 'https://s4.bukalapak.com/bukalapak-kontenz-production/content_attachments/72684/original/Esmeralda_Mobile_Legends.jpg', 'Esmeralda', 'Mage & Tank', 'Regen & Mixed Damage', 'Mid', 'Esmeralda, the enigmatic and versatile mage-tank of Mobile Legends, manipulated crystals and shields to protect her allies and disrupt her enemies. With her mystical abilities and ethereal presence, Esmeralda turned the tide of battle in her team\'s favor. Her ultimate ability, Inferno, absorbed enemy shields and converted them into her own, increasing her durability and damage output. Esmeralda\'s passive ability, Mystical Energy, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal bonus magic damage and steal enemy shields. Her ability to sustain through damage, provide crowd control, and absorb enemy shields made her a formidable mage-tank hybrid. Esmeralda\'s mysterious aura and her connection to the power of crystals made her a captivating and unpredictable hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Esmeralda\'s name became synonymous with arcane resilience and strategic versatility, forever etching her place as a mage-tank whose crystal manipulations shielded her allies and shattered her enemies.'),
(82, 'https://cms.hybrid.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/15d0cb1cd4a23b280a759d1a80462c72_Terizla_Default.jpg', 'Terizla', 'Fighter', 'Crowd Control & Burst', 'Exp', 'Terizla, the mighty and indomitable fighter of Mobile Legends, wielded his massive hammer with incredible strength and precision. With his exceptional power and durability, Terizla dominated the battlefield with his devastating attacks. His ultimate ability, Execution Strike, unleashed a powerful blow that stunned and dealt massive damage to enemies within its range. Terizla\'s passive ability, Charging Fist, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and slow enemy movement speed. His ability to initiate team fights, absorb damage, and deliver punishing blows made him a formidable force on the frontlines. Terizla\'s unwavering determination and his unyielding spirit made him a fearsome sight on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Terizla\'s name became synonymous with raw strength and unrelenting resolve, forever etching his place as a fighter whose hammer struck with earth-shattering force.'),
(83, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Mobile-Legends-X-Borg.jpg', 'X.Borg', 'Fighter', 'Regen & Burst', 'Exp', 'X.Borg, the fiery and relentless fighter of Mobile Legends, unleashed devastating flames upon his enemies with his flamethrower and mechanical suit. With his powerful arsenal and relentless aggression, X.Borg scorched the battlefield with his fiery abilities. His ultimate ability, Last Insanity, transformed him into an unstoppable inferno, dealing continuous damage and slowing enemies caught in his flames. X.Borg\'s passive ability, Firaga Armor, granted him enhanced durability and fire damage upon taking damage. His ability to dive into the heart of battle and unleash fiery devastation made him a formidable fighter. X.Borg\'s imposing presence and his affinity for fire made him a fearsome adversary. In the realm of Mobile Legends, X.Borg\'s name became synonymous with blazing fury and unyielding resilience, forever etching his place as a fighter whose flames engulfed his enemies.'),
(84, 'https://gamefinity.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Mobile-Legends-Ling.jpg', 'Ling', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Burst', 'Jungler', 'Ling, the agile and elusive assassin of Mobile Legends, soared through the battlefield with unmatched grace and agility. With his dual blades and acrobatic abilities, Ling struck fear into the hearts of his enemies. His ultimate ability, Tempest of Blades, allowed him to dash through enemies, dealing multiple strikes and leaving them vulnerable to his subsequent attacks. Ling\'s passive ability, Cloud Walker, granted him enhanced mobility and stealth, making him incredibly elusive and difficult to catch. His ability to swiftly eliminate targets and navigate the battlefield with unmatched agility made him a formidable assassin. Ling\'s mysterious nature and his mastery of aerial combat made him a captivating hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Ling\'s name became synonymous with aerial dominance and deadly precision, forever etching his place as an assassin whose blades danced through the air, leaving a trail of fallen foes in his wake.'),
(85, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/sites/2/2022/01/MLBB_Dyrroth.jpg', 'Dyrroth', 'Fighter', 'Charge & Burst', 'Exp', 'Dyrroth, the fierce and relentless fighter of Mobile Legends, brandished his massive Greatsword with unparalleled strength and skill. With his unrivaled power and unwavering determination, Dyrroth carved a path of destruction through the battlefield. His ultimate ability, Death\'s Sickle, unleashed a flurry of devastating slashes, dealing massive area-of-effect damage to enemies. Dyrroth\'s passive ability, Wrath of the Abyss, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and heal himself. His ability to engage in close combat, sustain through battles, and deliver devastating blows made him a formidable force. Dyrroth\'s imposing presence and his mastery of his Greatsword made him a fearsome opponent. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Dyrroth\'s name became synonymous with relentless aggression and unmatched power, forever etching his place as a fighter whose blade struck fear into the hearts of his enemies.'),
(86, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/11/03/59092352.jpg', 'Lylia', 'Mage', 'Push & Damage', 'Mid', 'Lylia, the whimsical and mystical mage of Mobile Legends, harnessed the power of her magic orbs to unleash devastating arcane attacks upon her enemies. With her otherworldly abilities and mysterious nature, Lylia turned the tide of battle with her incredible burst damage. Her ultimate ability, Feast, unleashed a barrage of magical orbs that followed enemies, dealing continuous damage and trapping them within a designated area. Lylia\'s passive ability, Magic Shadow, enhanced her movement speed and granted her increased damage on her next basic attack. Her ability to swiftly navigate the battlefield and rain down devastating magical attacks made her a formidable mage. Lylia\'s enchanting presence and her connection to the mystical realm made her a captivating hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Lylia\'s name became synonymous with arcane elegance and devastating precision, forever etching her place as a mage whose magical orbs brought chaos to her enemies.'),
(87, 'https://blog.unipin.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Trik-Maksimalkan-Baxia-Mobile-Legends-Demi-Bisa-GG.jpg', 'Baxia', 'Tank', 'Support & Damage', 'Roamer', 'Baxia, the resilient and stalwart tank of Mobile Legends, guarded his allies with unyielding determination and impenetrable defense. With his massive shield and sturdy armor, Baxia soaked up damage and disrupted enemy formations. His ultimate ability, Baxia\'s Shield, created a protective shield around himself, dealing damage and stunning enemies in the process. Baxia\'s passive ability, Tortoise\'s Puissance, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and regenerate his own HP. His ability to initiate team fights, absorb damage, and provide crowd control made him an invaluable asset to any team. Baxia\'s unwavering loyalty and his unbreakable resolve made him a true defender on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Baxia\'s name became synonymous with impenetrable defense and unyielding resilience, forever etching his place as a tank whose shield shielded his allies and shattered his enemies.'),
(88, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2022/03/25/858134852.jpg', 'Masha', 'Fighter & Tank', 'Push & Damage', 'Exp', 'Masha, the resilient and self-sustaining fighter of Mobile Legends, roamed the battlefield with unmatched stamina and endurance. With her multiple life bars and regenerative abilities, Masha proved to be a formidable force. Her ultimate ability, Life Recovery, allowed her to instantly restore a large portion of her health, enabling her to stay in fights for extended periods of time. Masha\'s passive ability, Ancient Strength, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal bonus damage and increase her movement speed. Her ability to split push, sustain through battles, and deal consistent damage made her a unique and versatile fighter. Masha\'s fierce independence and her tenacity in the face of adversity made her a fearsome opponent. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Masha\'s name became synonymous with unmatched stamina and indomitable spirit, forever etching her place as a fighter whose resilience knew no bounds.'),
(89, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/sites/2/2021/09/MLBB_Wanwan.jpg', 'Wanwan', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Wanwan, the agile and deadly marksman of Mobile Legends, utilized her twin crossbows to swiftly eliminate her enemies from a safe distance. With her exceptional mobility and precise attacks, Wanwan posed a constant threat on the battlefield. Her ultimate ability, Crossbow of Tang, allowed her to shoot multiple arrows simultaneously, dealing heavy damage to enemies within range. Wanwan\'s passive ability, Swallow\'s Path, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal bonus true damage and reduce enemy healing. Her ability to kite enemies, dodge incoming attacks, and deal consistent damage made her a force to be reckoned with. Wanwan\'s nimble movements and her unparalleled accuracy with her crossbows made her a captivating marksman. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Wanwan\'s name became synonymous with deadly precision and unparalleled agility, forever etching her place as a marksman whose arrows pierced through the hearts of her enemies.'),
(90, 'https://media.suara.com/pictures/970x544/2020/06/21/93138-hero-silvanna-moonton.jpg', 'Silvanna', 'Fighter', 'Initiator & Magic Damage', 'Exp', 'Silvanna, the charismatic and versatile fighter-tank of Mobile Legends, brought both elegance and power to the battlefield with her sword and shield. With her versatile kit and exceptional crowd control, Silvanna controlled the flow of battles and protected her allies. Her ultimate ability, Imperial Justice, unleashed a powerful burst of energy that pulled enemies towards her, stunning and damaging them. Silvanna\'s passive ability, Knightess Resolve, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal bonus damage and restore her own HP. Her ability to engage in team fights, initiate battles, and provide protection made her a valuable asset to any team composition. Silvanna\'s regal presence and her mastery of swordsmanship made her a captivating hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Silvanna\'s name became synonymous with unwavering justice and unyielding strength, forever etching her place as a fighter-tank whose sword defended her allies and struck down her enemies.'),
(91, 'https://cdn.vcgamers.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Carmilla-MLBB.jpg', 'Carmilla', 'Support', 'Crowd Control & Damage', 'Roamer', 'Carmilla, the alluring and versatile support of Mobile Legends, brought both elegance and darkness to the battlefield with her vampiric powers. With her crowd control and healing abilities, Carmilla protected her allies while draining the life force of her enemies. Her ultimate ability, Curse of Blood, immobilized enemies in an area and linked her own health to theirs, dealing damage and healing her allies in the process. Carmilla\'s passive ability, Shadow of Twilight, enhanced her basic attacks, allowing her to deal bonus magic damage and apply a mark that can be triggered for additional effects. Her ability to initiate team fights, provide crowd control, and sustain her team made her an invaluable support hero. Carmilla\'s captivating presence and her connection to the realm of darkness made her a force to be reckoned with. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Carmilla\'s name became synonymous with enchanting control and life-draining power, forever etching her place as a support whose shadows protected her allie'),
(92, 'https://media.suara.com/pictures/970x544/2022/05/25/76130-ilustrasi-skin-hero-cecilion-embrace-of-night.jpg', 'Cecilion', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Cecilion, the enigmatic and devastating mage of Mobile Legends, commanded the power of darkness to decimate his enemies. With his long-range attacks and area-of-effect abilities, Cecilion rained down destruction upon the battlefield. His ultimate ability, Moonlit Waltz, allowed him to teleport to a designated area, leaving behind a trail of dark energy that damaged enemies and increased his own magic power. Cecilion\'s passive ability, Overflowing, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus magic damage and regenerate his own HP. His ability to deal massive damage from a safe distance and control the battlefield made him a formidable mage. Cecilion\'s mysterious allure and his mastery of dark magic made him a captivating hero. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Cecilion\'s name became synonymous with devastating power and otherworldly elegance, forever etching his place as a mage whose darkness eclipsed his enemies.'),
(93, 'https://media-assets-ggwp.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/2022/07/sampul-3-640x360.jpg', 'Atlas', 'Tank & Support', 'Crowd Control & Initiator', 'Roamer', 'Atlas, the indomitable and unyielding tank of Mobile Legends, towered over the battlefield with his massive anchor and impenetrable armor. With his powerful crowd control and durability, Atlas protected his allies and disrupted enemy formations. His ultimate ability, Fatal Links, attached chains to enemies within a large area, damaging and stunning them while also slowing their movement speed. Atlas\'s passive ability, Fury of the Sea, enhanced his basic attacks, allowing him to deal bonus damage and reduce enemy healing. His ability to initiate team fights, absorb damage, and control the flow of battles made him a crucial asset to any team composition. Atlas\'s imposing presence and his unbreakable resolve made him a formidable force on the battlefield. In the realm of Mobile Legends, Atlas\'s name became synonymous with unyielding defense and unrelenting control, forever etching his place as a tank whose anchor weighed down his enemies and anchored his allies to victory.'),
(94, 'https://asset-a.grid.id/crop/34x18:1818x1217/x/photo/2020/04/22/2822033914.jpg', 'Popol & Kupa', 'Marksman', 'Push & Burst', 'Gold', 'Popol is a naughty boy who has ambitions and lofty ieals but is not understood. In order to prove himself, he went alone to hunt down the Icefield Dire Wolves, but accidentally fell into a trap. There was also an Dire Wolf called Kupa inside the trap. After a long time together, they developed a friendship and fought against a group of vultures together. Later, Popol and Kupa became the closest partners in the Ice Field.'),
(95, 'https://assets.skor.id/crop/0x0:0x0/x/photo/2021/05/01/3157341585.jpg', 'Yu Zhong', 'Fighter', 'Regen & Damage', 'Exp', 'A reincarnation of the Black Dragon, but Yu Zhong had no memory of the Black Dragon at first. After the Great Dragon accepted him as an apprentice, Yu Zhong went to the?Land of Dawn?in search of adventure where he met?Luo Yi?and was awakened by her. After that Yu Zhong rushed into the Forbidden Area to get back the reverse scale [belonging] to the Black Dragon and became the complete Black Dragon.'),
(96, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Luo-Yi-ML-Skin.jpg', 'Luo Yi', 'Mage', 'Support & Crowd Control', 'Mid', 'The Fighter attached to the Black Dragon. She was expelled from the Land of Dawn together with the Black Dragon after the Black Dragon failed. With a sense of mission to get freedom and the desire of her family to return to their homeland that had long lost, Luo Yi was determined to inherit her father\'s will. She would soon find the reincarnated Black Dragon, and possibly rebuild Fighter\'s glory.'),
(97, 'https://asset-a.grid.id/crop/0x0:1280x481/700x465/photo/2020/10/27/875436084.jpg', 'Benedetta', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Burst', 'Exp', 'After the rise of the Abyss, the land became plagued and the entire southern part of the?Land of Dawn?turned into a barren wasteland. Even though, the high ranged?Lantis Mountain?blocks the corruption of the Abyss, the Mother Nature in the southern realm continues to wither away. This once prosperous land is now nothing but a silent place filled with doom and death. People call it the?Despair Place. The only passage that connected the Crack of the Abyss with the Moniyan Empire was broken, separating the trapped refugees and the exiled wanderers from the rest of the world. They now live in fear and despair, haunted by monsters, yet struggling to survive. For these people, the name of Benedetta brought hope and a sense of security.'),
(98, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Hero-Khaleed-Cover-696x464.jpg', 'Khaleed', 'Fighter', 'Damage & Regen', 'Exp', 'There was an ancient tribe that lived in the endless deserts of?Agelta Drylands. They built villages along the?Emerald Road?and were able able to pass down their civilization and legacy, through countless generations. As the prince of the Artha Clan, Khaleed loved adventures. He longed to experience the once-glorious culture of the Emerald Road, dreaming that he could one day visit the vast Agelta Drylands and witness its prosperity. Ever since he was young, Khaleed would often take his squires with him, on an adventure along the Emerald Road. During their adventure, Khaleed met prince Moskov Moskov of the Wildsand Clan. The two equally brave young men shared the same passion for adventures, and quickly bonded with each other and developed a strong friendship. Together, they explored the entire Agetla Drylands.'),
(99, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/MLBB_Barats.jpg', 'Barats', 'Tank & Fighter', 'Damage & Crowd Control', 'Exp', 'Barats was born in such a Politan village, and he was born a naughty boy. Everyone in the village was annoyed by his trouble making nature. And such a childish personality didn\'t change even after Barats grew up. He had the same lust for money as his kind, but Barats hated learning and working. He would spend his entire day and free time, dreaming that he could miraculously get rich overnight. The villagers disliked Barats for his laziness, and they were subsequently thinking about chasing him out. This greatly angered Barats, who as a result sneaked into the village\'s sacred place, stole a precious item which was believed to be holy by everyone, and fled the place. The thing he stole was a treasure map. With the guidance of that treasure map, Barats arrived at the distant Albata. However, upon his arrival, he was disappointed by the what he saw.'),
(100, 'https://www.ligagame.tv/images/artikel/MLBB/brody-mlbb.jpg', 'Brody', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Burst', 'Gold', 'Brody lost his memory and wandered aimlessly between the villages of the Barren Lands, but there was always a voice in his heart asking him to hunt the Demons. In countless battles, Brody gradually recalled his past. Once, because of his mistakes, his village was massacred by the Demons and his right hand was also corroded. Now he understands his mission, in order to protect the people around him, Brody will always be fighting in a foreign land.');
INSERT INTO `heroes` (`id`, `images`, `names`, `roles`, `specialities`, `lane`, `desc`) VALUES
(101, 'https://dailyspin.id/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Yve-ML.jpg', 'Yve', 'Mage', 'Poke & Burst', 'Mid', 'Aurora?was the first person to discover Yve. This was the first time such a mysterious, cold, and emotionless creature had appeared in the?Land of Dawn. Massive energy fluctuations came from the time rift. Aurora thought that Zhask had returned and that she would finally have the chance to avenge her beloved. But as it turned out, she saw someone who seemed to be even more powerful. Yve came down from the sky above the Frozen Ocean. She considered everything and everyone beneath her notice and was only interested in finding Zhask. Her instincts told her that her old nemesis had once appeared here. Yve simply glanced at Aurora with indifference, then turned and left. Just as Aurora was hesitating about whether to chase down this mysterious visitor, Yve released an explosion of tremendous energy, closing the time rift temporarily. She then turned and left.'),
(102, 'https://api.duniagames.co.id/api/content/upload/file/14493814881600417819.jpg', 'Mathilda', 'Support & Assassin', 'Initiator & Guard', 'Roamer', 'The tribe where Mathilda lives has guarded the Holy Mountain for generations. Once, members of the tribe rescued a group of sand hunters under Kane, but unexpectedly they bit the hand that fed them by taking the Holy Mountain as their own. Mathilda was unafraid of their power. She left her hometown and met Clint. In the end, with the help of Clint, she was able to get her vengeance and return to the Holy Mountain with her tribe, inheriting the Holy Mountain\'s mysterious power.'),
(103, 'https://media.suara.com/pictures/653x366/2021/10/16/30022-paquito.jpg', 'Paquito', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Paquito was born in a small village in southwestern Moniyan. To survive and prosper in a land like this so far from the royal capital, you had to be strong. And so[,] he\'d had but one dream since he was a little boy: To become the world\'s strongest fighter. Paquito tempered his mind, his body and spirit through any and every means possible in his quest for this power. A reticent man passed through his village, witnessing the incredible effort Paquito was dedicating to his training. Hence[,] he decided to stay and trained Paquito, taking him as a student.'),
(104, 'https://oneesports.azureedge.net/cdn-data/2021/04/MLBB_Gloo.jpg', 'Gloo', 'Tank', 'Regen & Control', 'Exp', 'During a huge war waged in the?Barren Lands, the?Moniyan Empire\'s Second Regiment was almost entirely annihilated. Among the sea of corpses strewn all around, a Moniyan soldier had managed to survive; yet lost every one of his comrades, and was left to walk back to his homeland alone. Dark clouds shroud the Barren Lands year in, year out. Without the sun, moon and stars to guide his path, this solitary survivor lost his way and strayed into the Shadow Swamp. Both the earth and water found within the forests of the Shadow Swamp are corrupted by the Abyss, leaving the place moist and putrid. The man\'s extreme hunger and fatigue, together with the endless forest that surrounded him, plunged him into darkness and despair.'),
(105, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Hero-Phoveus-Cover.jpg', 'Phoveus', 'Fighter', 'Chase & Control', 'Exp', 'Phoveus was framed. Having been severely punished, he was then sent to fight with the vanguard. Once battle was over, Phoveus came across a most mysterious cage; and which was sealed the spirit of?Astaros, God of Terror. Bewitched by Astaros, Phoveus sacrificed his own two eyes in exchange for a great power, and now the two head ever deeper into the Dread Caves to awaken the body off that\'s numbers within.'),
(106, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/natan-mlbb-696x464.jpg', 'Natan', 'Marksman', 'Magic Damage & Burst', 'Gold', 'A thousand years after falling into a deep slumber, the Lord of the Abyss and the Lord of Light awoke, and so the Endless War raged once more. Natan stood as Eruditio\'s leader, guiding the people in their search for hope in this world. Yet having faced numerous defeats he decided instead to cast his gaze not to the future, but to the past—by inventing a time machine. As the world teetered on the brink of destruction, his time machine finally reached completion as it absorbed the combined power of the Twilight Orbs: Natan stepped within, and started searching the past for a chance to save the world.'),
(107, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Aulus-Hero-Cover.jpg', 'Aulus', 'Fighter', 'Damage & Crowd Control', 'Exp', 'Aulus longed to become a warrior, and for that, the other Leonins had taunted him and his battleaxe. To prove his powers, Aulus held back his rage, left his clan, and went on a journey to achieve great feats. But as a Leonin, all he ever faced was prejudice and injustice from the world. No longer able to bear it, Aulus headed toward the Lantis Mountains alone to hunt demons. Here, his strong rage awoke the slumbering battleaxe and henceforth they fought side by side to prove themselves, and the power of Leonins.'),
(108, 'https://cdn.mmoculture.com/mmo-images/2021/07/cbx4ybpjiwb71.png', 'Aamon', 'Assassin', 'Magic Damage & Burst', 'Mid', 'Aamon is the head of House Paxley and the current Duke of Castle Aberleen. Despite his cool and distant facade, he puts his kin above everything and will do anything for them. The child\'s father of Duke Paxley named him Aamon, and soon his younger brothers were born on after another. But as the eldest son and the family heir, Aamon had been subject to more strict discipline since his childhood. He was never allowed to be as free-spirited as his brother Gusion, and since as early as his boyhood, he\'d been occupied with studies and official duties all day. Aamon did not only learn the things required for a normal nobleman. His father Duke Paxley also secretly [teaches] him the spell that was only passed down to the family\'s direct descendants. It was a devious, ruthless spell that killed people neither honestly nor honorably. Aamon once felt skeptical because the secret family spell didn\'t match the honorable history of House Paxley that believed in the Lord of Light, and for this, he went out of his way to rea'),
(109, 'https://s2.bukalapak.com/bukalapak-kontenz-production/content_attachments/73932/original/Floryn_Mobile_Legends.jpg', 'Floryn', 'Support', 'Poke & Guard', 'Roamer', 'Belerick?stumbled upon the decline of?Agelta Drylands?during a meander of his many ago. The despair and sorrow almost consumed him, when a blooming little flower suddenly broke into his sight. \"There\'s still life!\" Moved by such tenacious vitality, the treant decided to create what was later known as the Oasis at the place.While creating the Oasis, Belerick unintentionally poured more power into the little flower, and the overflowing energy condensed into a glowing seed. The little flower, however, underwent an even more peculiar transition. It turned into a life form that had never appeared on the Land of Dawn?Floryn.'),
(110, 'https://oneesports.blob.core.windows.net/cdn-data/2021/03/MLBB_Beatrix.jpg', 'Beatrix', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'A year and a half ago, the Scholars\' Union of Eruditio welcomed a new student into their ranks. Unlike the other newcomers, this young girl named Beatrix seemed to possess profound knowledge of and astonishing talent for science. Before long she stood head and shoulders above her peers, becoming one of the most promising scholars of the entire Scholars\' Union. Even Dr. Rooney, who was watching her quietly from afar, was impressed by her progress. He believed that, if she were to apply herself to her studies, Beatrix could one day become the greatest scientist Eruditio had ever seen. Yet becoming the best scientist was not something Beatrix placed any great importance in. She was born in Castle Gorge in the Moniyan Empire, to a family of merchants. For generations, her family had already been well established as a wealthy merchant family business in the empire. In order to maintain their huge trade network, Beatrix\'s parents often had little choice but to travel all around the Land of Dawn on business, leaving'),
(111, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Mb3MzbALYN8/maxresdefault.jpg', 'Valentina', 'Mage', 'Reap & Burst', 'Mid', 'House Paxley?ruled over the regions near the?Lantis Mountains?in the south of the?Moniyan Empire. Generations of the house had guarded these areas for the Empire, defending against the invasion of the Abyss with magic and swords. As the house patriarch\'s eldest daughter, Valentina had been given high hopes since she was born. She underwent rigorous training and grew up into a proud perfectionist, the heir most qualified to lead this noble house. As she grew older, she went to the frontier and helped the house repel wave after wave of invading demons. The news of victories in Lantis Mountains became the only thing that could put the civilians\' minds at ease. As a result, House Paxley rose quickly among the nobles, while Valentina became the youngest and only female member of the house council.'),
(112, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/sites/2/2022/01/MLBB_Edith-min.jpg', 'Edith', 'Tank & Marksman', 'Control & Burst', 'Exp', 'Created by the Ancient Ones, Edith was the Primal Warden that watched over the sealed Evil Gods on the Sanctum Island. Awakened and injured in an earthquake, she lost her memories and was saved by her foster father who made a living by selling scraps and continued to raise her for ten years. When she once again helped her foster father enter the temple to search for scraps, the guardian of the ruins-Elemental Giant Uranus was prepared to destroy the invaders. It was then that Edith remembered everything, but her humanity overpowered her divine nature, and she fought Uranus to protect her foster father. Just then, the Celestial Palace fell and the sealed Evil Gods scattered. Edith parted with her foster father, drove her Mecha \"Phylax\" and set out on a journey to hunt down fleeing Evil Gods.'),
(113, 'https://cdn.oneesports.id/cdn-data/sites/2/2022/01/yin-1.jpg', 'Yin', 'Fighter', 'Control & Burst', 'Exp', 'Yin was an orphan found and raised by locals of Floral Falls. In an unfortunate incident, he ran into the fleeting?Evil God, Lieh and have since become the latter\'s a vessel. Although he\'d managed to regain control of his body, there was always the risk of the Evil God would break loose and wreak havoc up on everything he came into contact with. To protect his loved ones and hometown he embarked on the journey to?Moniyan Empire?alone in seeking a cure?'),
(114, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Hero-Melissa-Cover-696x464.jpg', 'Melissa', 'Marksman', 'Reap & Damage', 'Gold', 'There used to be an inconspicuous little tailor shop on the busy streets of the Lumina City, capital of the?Moniyan Empire. Its owner was an elegant woman always with a weary smile on her face, who had a clever, quirky daughter named Melissa. They lived a hard life, but Melissa always wore a clean, pretty dress and shoes, the worn-out parts carefully patched up in adorable patterns. She was naughty, but she was also thoughtful and sensible. When she was in the shop, she\'d help her mother with the needlework and put aside the shredded cloths. When she was old enough and already had enough worldly experience, she never asked again about where her dad was.'),
(115, 'https://i0.wp.com/esportsnesia.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Hero-Xavier-Cover.jpg', 'Xavier', 'Mage', 'Damage & Guard', 'Mid', 'Xavier was a member of the Knights of Light who was awarded the title \"Arbiter of Light\". After suppressing?Terizla\'s?Free Smiths\' Guild, Xavier underwent a decade of inner struggle and despondency. And when he was ordered to capture the two \"heretics\",?Yin?and?Melissa, he was once again forced to choose between duty and conscience?'),
(116, 'https://cdn.oneesports.gg/cdn-data/2022/04/MLBB_Julian.jpg', 'Julian', 'Fighter & Mage', 'Chase & Magic Damage', 'Exp', 'Julian was the son of?Terizla, the leader of the Free Smiths\' Guild. The guild was exterminated by the Church of Light on charges of heresy when Julian was at an early age. The poor child was then adopted by the archbishop, trained and molded to be an elite member of the Ravens, a secret force that listened only to the archbishop\'s orders. Later, on his mission to \"purify\" Xavier, he caught a glimpse of the secret buried in time?'),
(117, 'https://assets.skor.id/photo/2022/09/08/1304740607.jpg', 'Fredrinn', 'Tank & Fighter', 'Damage & Chase', 'Exp', 'Born the son of Duke Vance, Fredrinn grew up into a gifted adventurer, but also the notorious \'money-grubber\' in Los Pecados. The crystal in his chest had long merged with his heart. The terrifying scar would never fade, and Fredrinn never bothered to conceal it. All he had in mind was his search for his lost friend...'),
(118, 'https://foto.kontan.co.id/FiF63pBat3QRere8jwcpYnQu4ko=/smart/2022/11/15/1422701155p.jpg', 'Joy', 'Assassin', 'Chase & Damage', 'Exp', 'Agile and cunning, known as the most infamous \"petty thief\" in Lumina City, Joy had longed to have her stomach filled and her heart warmed. In a fortunate turn of events, Joy returned to the Leonins\' land, her wandering heart healed by the simple and unconditional love of her kin. She no longer feared losing love again and vowed to protect those around her, to turn into a golden flash resonating with home..'),
(119, 'https://foto.kontan.co.id/CRpQ36NsWAkUVC2-NFN2X3fqpkc=/smart/2023/01/23/1789503733p.jpg', 'Arlott', 'Fighter & Assassin', 'Charge & Burst', 'Exp', 'Ostracized for this half-demon and half-human lineage, the young Arlott joined the Demons in the Barren Lands but was betrayed by his demonic brethren during battle. However, after he was gravely wounded, he was saved by a human girl named Mila. During their time together, Mila\'s innocence and sincerity gradually changed his view on humans. This was not to last, however, as the Church of Light executed Mira for heresy. Arlott slaughtered every living soul in the Church before he laid Mila\'s body to rest in the lakeside forest.');
